.DT
set_cond
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_cond

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_cond -  This method sets the current condition of the object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_cond(int i)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^i%^RESET%^ - the new condition
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/condition.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the current condition of the object.  If this is lower
than the current lowest conditon, then the lowest condition will be modified
to be this.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
adjust_condition

.EP

